# Coding Conventions

Use `function` keyword by default. Arrow functions only for callbacks or returned functions:
- ✓ `function handleClick() {}`
- ✓ `someArray.map(item => doSomething(item))`
- ✓ `function factory() { return (x) => x * 2 }`